Or Login / Register With Us Forgot Password? Remember Me Yewon goes sporty for 'Addy K' By jennywill 19 minutes ago 1,472 66 0 0 Google+ Yewon had a sporty photoshoot for ' Addy K '!
She put on sporty outfits, shorts, leggings, and more to pull off an athletic photoshoot. Even with the tight outfits, she boasted of an envious figure that was made through her continuously taking care of her body. 
She said, " I'm more into unique characters that'll make people think, 'how can she make herself like that?' instead of quiet, feminine characters. "
